'''丙烯酸'''，又稱'''壓克力酸'''，是最简单的[[不饱和|不饱和]][[羧酸|羧酸]]。其化学式为[[碳|C]]<sub>3</sub>[[氢|H]]<sub>4</sub>[[氧|O]]<sub>2</sub>，由一个[[乙烯基|乙烯基]]和一个[[羧基|羧基]]构成。纯丙烯酸是无色澄清液体，具有特殊刺激性气味，可与水、[[乙醇|乙醇]]、[[乙醚|乙醚]]和[[氯仿|氯仿]]互溶。丙烯酸可由炼油厂提炼的[[丙烯|丙烯]]制备；以更廉价的原料[[丙烷|丙烷]]选择性氧化制备丙烯酸的工艺，目前尚待深入研究<ref>{{cite journal |title=The reaction network in propane oxidation over phase-pure MoVTeNb M1 oxide catalysts |journal=Journal of Catalysis |date=2014 |volume=311 |page=369-385 |url=https://pure.mpg.de/rest/items/item_1896844_6/component/file_1896843/content |access-date=2019-04-26 |archive-date=2020-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713133050/https://pure.mpg.de/rest/items/item_1896844_6/component/file_1896843/content |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |title=Surface chemistry of phase-pure M1 MoVTeNb oxide during operation in selective oxidation of propane to acrylic acid |journal=Journal of Catalysis |date=2012 |volume=285 |issue=285 |page=48-60 |url=https://pure.mpg.de/rest/items/item_1108560_8/component/file_1402724/content |access-date=2019-04-26 |archive-date=2020-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713133044/https://pure.mpg.de/rest/items/item_1108560_8/component/file_1402724/content |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |editor=Kinetic studies of propane oxidation on Mo and V based mixed oxide catalysts |date=2011 |url=https://pure.mpg.de/rest/items/item_1199619_5/component/file_1199618/content |title= |chapter=存档副本 |access-date=2019-04-26 |archive-date=2020-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200519081200/https://pure.mpg.de/rest/items/item_1199619_5/component/file_1199618/content |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |title=Multifunctionality of Crystalline MoV(TeNb) M1 Oxide Catalysts in Selective Oxidation of Propane and Benzyl Alcoho |journal=ACS Catalysis |date=2013 |volume=3 (6) |page=1103-1113 |url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/278196177_Multifunctionality_of_Crystalline_MoVTeNb_M1_Oxide_Catalysts_in_Selective_Oxidation_of_Propane_and_Benzyl_Alcohol |access-date=2019-04-26 |archive-date=2019-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329172554/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/278196177_Multifunctionality_of_Crystalline_MoVTeNb_M1_Oxide_Catalysts_in_Selective_Oxidation_of_Propane_and_Benzyl_Alcohol |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

丙烯酸具有[[羧酸|羧酸]]的一般性质，可与[[醇|醇]]反应得到相应的[[酯|酯]]。常用的丙烯酸酯包括[[丙烯酸甲酯|丙烯酸甲酯]]、[[丙烯酸丁酯|丙烯酸丁酯]]、[[丙烯酸乙酯|丙烯酸乙酯]]和[[丙烯酸-2-乙基己酯|丙烯酸-2-乙基己酯]]。

丙烯酸及其酯类自身或与其他[[单体|单体]]混合后，会发生[[聚合反应|聚合反应]]生成[[均聚物|均聚物]]或[[共聚物|共聚物]]。通常可与丙烯酸共聚的单体包括[[酰胺|酰胺]]类、[[丙烯腈|丙烯腈]]、含[[乙烯基|乙烯基]]类、[[苯乙烯|苯乙烯]]和[[丁二烯|丁二烯]]等。这类聚合物可用于生产各式[[塑料|塑料]]、[[涂层|涂层]]、[[粘合剂|粘合剂]]、[[弹性体|弹性体]]、地板擦光剂及涂料<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fpc.com.tw/fpcw/index.php?op=proL&f=1&s=90 |language=zh-hant |title=丙稀酸酯 |publisher=台灣塑膠工業股份有限公司 |accessdate=2018-11-30 |archive-date=2018-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181130071820/http://www.fpc.com.tw/fpcw/index.php?op=proL&f=1&s=90 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 安全 ==
丙烯酸有很强的刺激性辛辣气味，对皮肤有强烈刺激性及腐蚀性。眼部接触可能会造成无法治愈的角膜烧伤，吸入相当量的蒸汽可能会对呼吸系统造成刺激，导致昏睡或头痛。少量接触危害不大，但高浓度的接触可能会引起[[肺水肿|肺水肿]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.somsds.com/detail.asp?id=1475193126 |language=zh-hans |title=丙稀酸安全技術說明書 |publisher=somsds |accessdate=2018-11-30 |archive-date=2018-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181130212051/http://www.somsds.com/detail.asp?id=1475193126 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

